## Data Source Note
Due to limitations of free real-time Hong Kong stock market APIs, this demo uses sophisticated market simulation that:
- Generates realistic price movements based on historical volatility patterns
- Updates hourly with new data
- Maintains consistent technical indicators (RSI, Moving Averages)
- Simulates market trends and volatility

For production deployment with real data, integration with paid APIs like Bloomberg, Reuters, or HKEX datafeed would be required.

# HK Stock AI Analysis System

## üöÄ Live Demo
- Production: https://stock-ai-hk-6wox.vercel.app
- API Docs: https://web-production-387c9.up.railway.app/docs

## üìä Features
- Real-time Hong Kong stock data analysis (5 major stocks)
- AI-powered technical analysis with scoring system
- Risk assessment (Low/Moderate/High/Very High)
- Sentiment analysis from news articles
- Interactive dashboard with auto-refresh
- RESTful API with FastAPI

## üõ†Ô∏è Tech Stack
- **Backend**: Python, FastAPI, yfinance
- **AI/ML**: Custom technical indicators, sentiment analysis
- **Frontend**: HTML5, JavaScript, responsive design
- **Deployment**: Railway (API), Vercel (Frontend)

## üìà Analyzed Stocks
- 0700.HK - Tencent
- 9988.HK - Alibaba
- 0005.HK - HSBC
- 0941.HK - China Mobile
- 1299.HK - AIA Group

## üî¨ Analysis Components
1. **Technical Analysis** (60% weight)
   - RSI, MACD, Bollinger Bands
   - Moving averages (SMA20)
   - Volume analysis

2. **Sentiment Analysis** (40% weight)
   - News article processing
   - TextBlob sentiment scoring

3. **Risk Assessment**
   - Volatility analysis
   - Support/resistance levels
   - Combined risk scoring

## üö¶ Data Sources
- **Local Development**: Real-time data via yfinance
- **Production**: Simulated data (due to cloud limitations)
- **News**: NewsAPI (when API key available)

Built in 3 days as a portfolio project for HK fintech opportunities.

